TEXT 344 -384 Left 2 !.model SW SW(Ron=1m Roff=1G Vt=0.5 Vh=0.1)
TEXT -400 -632 Left 2 !.param in_amplitude=0.3
TEXT -400 -600 Left 2 !.param in_freq=1000
TEXT -400 -344 Left 2 !.options plotwinsize=0
TEXT -24 664 Left 2 !.param t_start = 100m\n.param tran_window = 10 / {in_freq}\n.param t_stop = {t_start + tran_window}\n.param step = 1 / {1000 * in_freq}\n.tran {step} {t_stop} {t_start} {step}
TEXT -1816 -400 Left 2 !* --- 1. Node Voltages & THD ---\n* Analiza niveles de seńal, offsets DC y distorsión armónica en cada etapa.\n.meas tran Vin_mean AVG V(in)\n.meas tran Vin_max MAX V(in)\n.meas tran Vin_min MIN V(in)\n.meas tran Vin_rms RMS V(in)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(in)\n.meas tran Vq1b_mean AVG V(Q1B)\n.meas tran Vq1b_max MAX V(Q1B)\n.meas tran Vq1b_min MIN V(Q1B)\n.meas tran Vq1b_rms RMS V(Q1B)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q1B)\n.meas tran Vq1e_mean AVG V(Q1E)\n.meas tran Vq1e_max MAX V(Q1E)\n.meas tran Vq1e_min MIN V(Q1E)\n.meas tran Vq1e_rms RMS V(Q1E)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q1E)\n.meas tran Vq2e_mean AVG V(Q2E)\n.meas tran Vq2e_max MAX V(Q2E)\n.meas tran Vq2e_min MIN V(Q2E)\n.meas tran Vq2e_rms RMS V(Q2E)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q2E)\n.meas tran Vq2c_mean AVG V(Q2C)\n.meas tran Vq2c_max MAX V(Q2C)\n.meas tran Vq2c_min MIN V(Q2C)\n.meas tran Vq2c_rms RMS V(Q2C)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q2C)\n.meas tran Vmidin_mean AVG V(MID_IN)\n.meas tran Vmidin_max MAX V(MID_IN)\n.meas tran Vmidin_min MIN V(MID_IN)\n.meas tran Vmidin_rms RMS V(MID_IN)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(MID_IN)\n.meas tran Vtonein_mean AVG V(TONE_IN)\n.meas tran Vtonein_max MAX V(TONE_IN)\n.meas tran Vtonein_min MIN V(TONE_IN)\n.meas tran Vtonein_rms RMS V(TONE_IN)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(TONE_IN)\n.meas tran Vtoneout_mean AVG V(TONE_OUT)\n.meas tran Vtoneout_max MAX V(TONE_OUT)\n.meas tran Vtoneout_min MIN V(TONE_OUT)\n.meas tran Vtoneout_rms RMS V(TONE_OUT)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(TONE_OUT)\n.meas tran Vq3b_mean AVG V(Q3B)\n.meas tran Vq3b_max MAX V(Q3B)\n.meas tran Vq3b_min MIN V(Q3B)\n.meas tran Vq3b_rms RMS V(Q3B)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q3B)\n.meas tran Vq3e_mean AVG V(Q3E)\n.meas tran Vq3e_max MAX V(Q3E)\n.meas tran Vq3e_min MIN V(Q3E)\n.meas tran Vq3e_rms RMS V(Q3E)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q3E)\n.meas tran Vq3c_mean AVG V(Q3C)\n.meas tran Vq3c_max MAX V(Q3C)\n.meas tran Vq3c_min MIN V(Q3C)\n.meas tran Vq3c_rms RMS V(Q3C)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q3C)\n.meas tran Vq4e_mean AVG V(Q4E)\n.meas tran Vq4e_max MAX V(Q4E)\n.meas tran Vq4e_min MIN V(Q4E)\n.meas tran Vq4e_rms RMS V(Q4E)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q4E)\n.meas tran Vout_mean AVG V(OUT)\n.meas tran Vout_max MAX V(OUT)\n.meas tran Vout_min MIN V(OUT)\n.meas tran Vout_rms RMS V(OUT)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(OUT)\n* --- 2. Current Draw & DC Bias ---\n* Crucial para consumo y puntos de operación de los transistores.\n.meas tran I_Supply_mean AVG I(V2)\n.meas tran Power_Total_mW PARAM abs(I_Supply_mean*15)*1000\n.meas tran Iq1_bias AVG I(R8)\n.meas tran Iq3_bias AVG I(R22)\n* --- 3. Stage-by-Stage AC Gains & Losses ---\n* Usa valores peak-to-peak para ignorar offsets de DC.\n.meas tran Gain_Stage1 PARAM (Vq2c_max-Vq2c_min)/(Vin_max-Vin_min)\n.meas tran Tone_Loss PARAM (Vtoneout_max-Vtoneout_min)/(Vtonein_max-Vtonein_min)\n.meas tran Tone_Loss_dB PARAM 20*log10(Tone_Loss)\n.meas tran Gain_Stage2 PARAM (Vout_max-Vout_min)/(Vtoneout_max-Vtoneout_min)\n* --- 4. Impedance Measurements ---\n* 1. Impedancia de entrada (Zin)\n.meas tran Iin_peak MAX I(V1)\n.meas tran Iin_val_min MIN I(V1)\n.meas tran Zin_large PARAM (Vin_max-Vin_min)/(Iin_peak-Iin_val_min)\n* 2. Impedancia de salida de la Etapa 1 (hacia el Tone Stack)\n.meas tran Ic4_peak MAX I(C4)\n.meas tran Ic4_min MIN I(C4)\n.meas tran Zout_stage1 PARAM (Vq2c_max-Vq2c_min)/(Ic4_peak-Ic4_min)\n* 3. Impedancia de salida efectiva del pedal\n.meas tran Iout_peak MAX I(C12)\n.meas tran Iout_min MIN I(C12)\n.meas tran Zout_eff PARAM (Vout_max-Vout_min)/(Iout_peak-Iout_min)\n* --- 5. Diode Clipping Characterization ---\n.meas tran Idiodes_peak MAX I(D1)\n.meas tran P_clipping AVG V(TONE_IN)*I(D1)\n.meas tran Clip_Symmetry_Diodes PARAM (Vtonein_max/abs(Vtonein_min))\n* --- 6. Overall Gain & Symmetry ---\n.meas tran Voltage_Gain_rms PARAM Vout_rms/Vin_rms\n.meas tran Voltage_Gain PARAM Vout_max/Vin_max\n.meas tran Clip_Symmetry_Out PARAM (Vout_max/abs(Vout_min))\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 I(C12)\n.meas tran Ic10_peak MAX I(C10)\n.meas tran Ic10_min MIN I(C10)\n.meas tran Zin_stage2 PARAM (Vtoneout_max-Vtoneout_min)/(Ic10_peak-Ic10_min)\n* --- 7. BJT Bootstrap Input Buffer Metrics ---\n* Evaluando la salud y ganancia de la etapa Bootstrap (Q5)\n.meas tran Vq5b_mean AVG V(Q5B)\n.meas tran Vq5b_max MAX V(Q5B)\n.meas tran Vq5b_min MIN V(Q5B)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q5B)\n.meas tran Vq5e_mean AVG V(Q5E)\n.meas tran Vq5e_max MAX V(Q5E)\n.meas tran Vq5e_min MIN V(Q5E)\n.four {in_freq} 10 10 V(Q5E)\n.meas tran Vq5_bias_mean AVG V(Q5_BIAS)\n* Ganancia del Seguidor de Emisor (Target: ~0.98x)\n.meas tran Gain_Buffer PARAM (Vq5e_max-Vq5e_min)/(Vq5b_max-Vq5b_min)\n* --- 8. Power Rail & Efficiency Analysis ---\n* Verificando el consumo incluyendo el nuevo buffer\n.meas tran Vq4c_mean AVG V(Q4C)\n.meas tran vq4c_max MAX V(Q4C)\n.meas tran vq4c_min MIN V(Q4C)\n.meas tran Vq4c_ripple PARAM (vq4c_max-vq4c_min)\n.meas tran Iq5_bias AVG I(R18)\n.meas tran Iq4_bias AVG I(R2)\n* --- 9. Transient & Linearity Performance ---\n* Slew Rate y Headroom\n.meas tran Rise_Time TRIG V(OUT)=0.1*Vout_max RISE=1 TARG V(OUT)=0.9*Vout_max RISE=1\n.meas tran Slew_Rate PARAM (0.8*Vout_max)/Rise_Time\n.meas tran Headroom_Pos PARAM (Vq4c_mean-Vout_max)\n.meas tran Headroom_Neg PARAM (Vout_min-0)\n.meas tran Vq5b_rms RMS V(Q5B)\n.meas tran Vq5e_rms RMS V(Q5E)
TEXT 976 -216 Left 2 !.param P4b = potrevlog_b(1k, drive)
TEXT 984 -392 Left 2 !.func potrevlog_a(ohm, rot) {ohm * (1 - ((1 - rot) ** 3.3)) + 1m}
TEXT 984 -360 Left 2 !.func potrevlog_b(ohm, rot) {ohm * ((1 - rot) ** 3.3) + 1m}
